20:58.391 --> 21:00.524
â™ª oh

21:00.526 --> 21:02.927
â™ª I don't want to be alone

21:02.929 --> 21:05.663
â™ª I want to find a home

21:05.665 --> 21:08.466
â™ª and I want to share it
with you â™ª

21:10.335 --> 21:12.837
I'm all right.

21:12.839 --> 21:16.674
â™ª hello, my own heart

21:16.676 --> 21:18.609
â™ª it's been so long

21:18.611 --> 21:22.546
â™ª since I've given you away

21:22.548 --> 21:27.885
â™ª and every day
I add another stone â™ª

21:27.887 --> 21:30.421
