21:30.423 --> 21:32.423
Louis,

21:32.425 --> 21:34.292
I think...
It's enough for now.

21:34.294 --> 21:36.894
For now.

21:46.772 --> 21:48.839
Did I fall asleep?

21:52.778 --> 21:55.780
That was...

21:55.782 --> 21:57.848
You are talented.

21:59.785 --> 22:01.852
You were so
lost in it.

22:03.822 --> 22:06.524
Was that what
you wanted?

22:06.526 --> 22:09.727
To lose yourself?

22:09.729 --> 22:11.729
You are quite lovely,
lady amelie.

22:11.731 --> 22:12.863
Thank you.

22:13.699 --> 22:15.700
I have to go.

22:15.702 --> 22:17.001
Will you be all right?

22:27.679 --> 22:29.714
(gasps)

22:29.716 --> 22:31.015
(giggles)

22:31.017 --> 22:32.450
What was that for?

22:32.452 --> 22:33.884
Fun. What of it?
(gasps)

22:33.886 --> 22:35.686
That's enough of that.

22:46.365 --> 22:48.899
We've been seen.

22:53.972 --> 22:55.773
Who was that woman?
She saw us together.

22:55.775 --> 22:57.775
She could tell anyone--
it would mean our heads.

22:57.777 --> 22:58.809
She won't.

22:58.811 --> 23:00.077
Go back
to the castle.

23:00.079 --> 23:02.613
Wait for me there.

23:02.615 --> 23:03.981
Conde:
Hyah! Hyah! Hyah!

23:03.983 --> 23:05.549
Hyah!

23:10.021 --> 23:11.522
Conde:
Who are you?

23:11.524 --> 23:13.657
What is your business
in these parts?

23:19.431 --> 23:20.498
Antoine.

23:20.500 --> 23:21.766
You can't honestly
be surprised

23:21.768 --> 23:24.168
That I protected
my own interests.

23:24.170 --> 23:25.870
After you balked at your meeting
with elizabeth's envoy,

23:25.872 --> 23:28.105
I had you followed.

23:28.107 --> 23:29.173
You may go.

23:30.709 --> 23:32.042
And don't worry--

23:32.044 --> 23:33.577
She's loyal to me.

23:33.579 --> 23:34.645
Your secret's safe.

23:34.647 --> 23:35.946
For now.

23:35.948 --> 23:37.715
Is that a threat?

23:37.717 --> 23:39.617
You're jeopardizing your future,
our family's future.

23:39.619 --> 23:41.018
You must end your affair
with mary.

23:41.020 --> 23:42.153
I will not.

23:42.155 --> 23:43.721
You will do
what your family needs.

23:43.723 --> 23:45.423
Or I will tell francis
all that I know

23:45.425 --> 23:46.657
Of you and his wife.

23:46.659 --> 23:48.659
He will cut off
my head, antoine.

23:48.661 --> 23:49.860
Who will get you
elizabeth then?

23:49.862 --> 23:51.862
Well, you won't help me now.

23:51.864 --> 23:53.864
Why should I think you'll help
me if I let you live?

23:53.866 --> 23:56.100
And remember, if the nobles
learn of the affair,

23:56.102 --> 23:59.170
The law demands
mary's head, too.

23:59.172 --> 24:02.440
Will you risk mary's life
for a few nights of passion?

24:02.442 --> 24:03.707
You have two hours.

24:03.709 --> 24:06.811
End it with mary,
or I will end both of you.

24:10.882 --> 24:13.551
Well, you couldn't be with him
when he was a kitchen servant

24:13.553 --> 24:14.852
And you were
a queen's lady.

24:14.854 --> 24:16.720
That I understand.

24:16.722 --> 24:18.122
But now it's different.

24:18.124 --> 24:19.957
He's an officer
of the kingsguard, and...

24:19.959 --> 24:21.459
I'm married.

24:21.461 --> 24:22.827
Now and forever.

24:22.829 --> 24:24.695
It's wrong and
scandalous.

24:24.697 --> 24:27.031
And you would be ruined.
Aren't you already?

24:27.033 --> 24:29.767
It's not the worst thing
in the world, is it?

24:31.002 --> 24:32.236
Is that your man now?

24:34.973 --> 24:37.675
Yes, but he's
not my man.

24:40.178 --> 24:41.745
You judge apples
by color.

24:41.747 --> 24:43.781
Also firmness.

24:43.783 --> 24:45.683
Like this one.

24:47.018 --> 24:48.018
Leith.

24:48.020 --> 24:49.153
What...

24:49.155 --> 24:50.588
What are you doing here?

24:50.590 --> 24:51.889
I wanted to offer
my friendship.

24:51.891 --> 24:54.124
If you should ever need
help with anything--

24:54.126 --> 24:56.660
Companionship,
rent money,

24:56.662 --> 24:59.864
Produce selection...
Anything.

24:59.866 --> 25:01.031
I know you're cut
off from the castle,

25:01.033 --> 25:02.199
But you're never
cut off from me.

25:02.201 --> 25:03.901
That's truly kind.

25:03.903 --> 25:07.238
I'm sorry I dismissed you
so abruptly before.

25:07.240 --> 25:11.008
I guess I was overcome
by pride-- foolish pride.

25:11.010 --> 25:12.943
Hands off, pig!

25:12.945 --> 25:14.912
I don't owe you
no poke or no tug.

25:14.914 --> 25:15.980
Man:
Shut up!

25:18.517 --> 25:21.519
You heard the girl--
take your hands off her.

25:21.521 --> 25:23.287
Don't make me waste
another perfectly good apple.

25:23.289 --> 25:24.288
They're very expensive.

25:24.290 --> 25:25.756
Leave us alone!

25:25.758 --> 25:27.124
Be a gentleman, sir,

25:27.126 --> 25:28.292
And let go of her.

25:28.294 --> 25:30.528
I said it's none
of your business.

25:32.697 --> 25:33.931
Actually, it is
my business.

25:33.933 --> 25:36.133
Gigi is my neighbor,
my friend and...

25:36.135 --> 25:38.102
You mean she's
one of your whores?

25:38.104 --> 25:40.838
I've seen you pocket
your take from them.

25:40.840 --> 25:42.573
You tell your whore
she ain't done her job,

25:42.575 --> 25:44.775
And I want what's mine,
one way or another.

25:44.777 --> 25:47.978
You'll step away from gigi now,
or everyone here will understand

25:47.980 --> 25:49.980
Why the working girls
call you "old shrivel."

25:50.982 --> 25:52.149
Would you like that, sir?

25:52.151 --> 25:54.852
(laughter)

25:54.854 --> 25:56.320
Who needs you?

25:56.322 --> 25:58.289
Out of my way.
You all right?

25:58.291 --> 26:00.190
Thank you.

26:00.192 --> 26:02.159
You showed him, greer.

26:19.311 --> 26:20.978
Did you find the woman?

26:20.980 --> 26:23.180
She led me straight to
the man she works for.

26:23.182 --> 26:25.182
The man who sent
her to follow me.

26:25.184 --> 26:26.684
Follow you?

26:26.686 --> 26:28.118
Who was it? Francis?

26:28.120 --> 26:29.353
My brother.

26:29.355 --> 26:31.121
Antoine knows about us?

26:31.123 --> 26:33.123
About scotland?

26:33.125 --> 26:34.959
Nothing of
scotland, not yet.

26:34.961 --> 26:36.961
Why would he have
you followed?

26:36.963 --> 26:38.696
Does he suspect you
of something?

26:38.698 --> 26:40.197
Is-is there some issue
between the two of you?

26:40.199 --> 26:41.732
My brother
seeks advantage

26:41.734 --> 26:43.233
Whenever he can.

26:43.235 --> 26:44.735
And now he has it.

26:44.737 --> 26:46.337
Mary, we need
to reconsider our plans--

26:46.339 --> 26:47.338
Scotland, all of it.

26:47.340 --> 26:49.006
Why?

26:49.008 --> 26:51.742
Antoine said that
if we don't break it off,

26:51.744 --> 26:53.143
He'll tell francis
what he knows.

26:53.145 --> 26:54.745
It would cost you your head.

26:54.747 --> 26:56.614
Why would he risk your
life to keep us apart?

26:56.616 --> 26:58.682
I... I don't know.

26:59.684 --> 27:01.185
Then we must face reality.

27:02.887 --> 27:04.355
We cannot be together,
not now.

27:04.357 --> 27:06.890
And as much as I want you,

27:06.892 --> 27:09.026
I will not risk your
life to be with you.

27:09.028 --> 27:11.161
I'm so sorry.

27:11.163 --> 27:15.165
I would have given anything
to go on the way we were.

27:15.167 --> 27:17.034
To join you in scotland.

27:17.036 --> 27:19.970
I know.

27:32.083 --> 27:34.685
Forgive me,
but you look ghastly.

27:34.687 --> 27:37.788
Yes, well, I've felt better.

27:37.790 --> 27:38.956
When I've had
more sleep.

27:38.958 --> 27:40.658
I saw you leave
the tasting last night

27:40.660 --> 27:41.792
With narcisse's niece.

27:41.794 --> 27:43.193
She came back hours later,
all smiles.

27:43.195 --> 27:45.195
And you never
came back at all.

27:45.197 --> 27:46.330
Lola, don't.

27:46.332 --> 27:48.232
Don't give up on her, francis.

27:48.234 --> 27:50.701
I know mary's
pushing you away,

27:50.703 --> 27:51.835
But given
what she's been through,

27:51.837 --> 27:52.970
It's what she needs to do.

27:52.972 --> 27:55.339
All she needs is time.

27:55.341 --> 27:57.341
You, you sound
exactly like me,

27:57.343 --> 27:59.343
And like me,
you're wrong.

27:59.345 --> 28:01.111
Mary doesn't
want time.

28:01.113 --> 28:03.981
What she wants
is condÃ©.

28:03.983 --> 28:05.716
No.

28:05.718 --> 28:07.918
No, she admitted it, lola.
She wants to be with him.

28:07.920 --> 28:10.187
I forbade it, of course. Can you
imagine what that was like?

28:10.189 --> 28:12.356
Telling my wife, after
all she's been through,

28:12.358 --> 28:14.058
That no, she cannot
have the one thing

28:14.060 --> 28:15.759
She believes will
make her happy.

28:15.761 --> 28:17.161
An affair that would
get her killed.

28:17.163 --> 28:19.163
Look, I know this must hurt.

28:19.165 --> 28:21.331
But if you can't dissuade mary
from this course,

28:21.333 --> 28:24.001
Then you owe it to her to do
what you can to protect her.

28:24.003 --> 28:25.469
As a king,
you can squash rumors,

28:25.471 --> 28:27.037
And if that fails,

28:27.039 --> 28:29.006
You can shield them
from the severest punishment.

28:29.008 --> 28:30.274
It is a betrayal.

28:30.276 --> 28:32.276
Do you think mary turns
to condÃ© to hurt you?

28:32.278 --> 28:34.978
She loves you.

28:34.980 --> 28:37.314
She does what she does because
she sees no other option.

28:37.316 --> 28:39.917
She's desperate to get past
her pain, to heal.

28:39.919 --> 28:43.253
So I should stand by, a king,

28:43.255 --> 28:46.123
And grant my wife free rein
to be with another man?

28:46.125 --> 28:47.958
I don't know, francis.

28:47.960 --> 28:50.294
It depends on how much
you love her.

28:50.296 --> 28:52.763
And how much
you want her to heal.

28:53.898 --> 28:55.499
And to heal yourself.

29:00.004 --> 29:02.773
Majesty, your queen has arrived,
and she bids that you join her.

29:02.775 --> 29:03.774
Jeanne?

29:03.776 --> 29:05.042
She's here? Since when?

29:05.044 --> 29:06.343
She arrived
a few minutes ago.

29:09.013 --> 29:10.881
(jeanne gasps)
antoine: Hurry.

29:10.883 --> 29:12.149
My wife needs a chair.

29:12.151 --> 29:13.383
Woman: Your grace.
Woman 2: My lady.

29:13.385 --> 29:14.785
Woman 3: Some water!
Man: Water!

29:14.787 --> 29:16.186
Antoine: Are you all
right, my darling?

29:23.294 --> 29:25.229
Give me one moment.

29:28.800 --> 29:30.801
Kenna, please stop.

29:30.803 --> 29:32.803
Listen.

29:32.805 --> 29:34.171
Whatever you think you may know,

29:34.173 --> 29:35.305
My wife is pregnant, yes,

29:35.307 --> 29:36.774
But she's still
very ill.

29:36.776 --> 29:37.808
That's why I sent for her--
I thought

29:37.810 --> 29:38.809
She might want to meet you...

29:38.811 --> 29:40.177
Enough!

29:40.179 --> 29:42.312
You didn't invite her. I did.

29:42.314 --> 29:44.948
I had to see this illness
of hers for myself.

29:44.950 --> 29:46.550
So you were testing my story.

29:46.552 --> 29:48.051
Bash was right.

29:48.053 --> 29:49.453
Your only intention
was vengeance

29:49.455 --> 29:51.188
On him for killing your brother.

29:51.190 --> 29:54.424
You never intended to marry
me, not for one moment.

29:54.426 --> 29:56.426
Just to bed me,

29:56.428 --> 29:58.095
To punish my husband.

29:58.097 --> 29:59.229
You're right.

29:59.231 --> 30:00.464
It began that way,

30:00.466 --> 30:01.932
But I do want you.

30:01.934 --> 30:03.333
As what?!

30:03.335 --> 30:05.836
I thought I'd convince you
to be my mistress.

30:05.838 --> 30:07.838
Because I'd be ruined.

30:07.840 --> 30:11.208
And... My husband humiliated.

30:11.210 --> 30:15.078
Well, I can't deny hoping
for that last bit.

30:15.080 --> 30:18.182
You judge me, but you don't
know who these people are.

30:18.184 --> 30:20.117
They've committed
atrocities.

30:20.119 --> 30:21.518
Murder by the thousands.

30:21.520 --> 30:23.387
They are rulers.
This is the price they pay.

30:23.389 --> 30:25.088
You can still
leave with me.

30:25.090 --> 30:27.491
I will love you
and make you happy.

30:27.493 --> 30:28.959
I am happy!

30:28.961 --> 30:30.894
And I love my husband.

30:33.865 --> 30:37.234
If my wife had arrived
gravely ill,

30:37.236 --> 30:38.602
You'd have left your husband.

30:38.604 --> 30:42.005
Your marriage is
already over.

30:42.007 --> 30:44.208
You just don't know it yet.

30:55.486 --> 30:57.421
Francis, we
need to talk.
I know.

30:57.423 --> 30:59.256
I was going to come and find you

30:59.258 --> 31:01.325
Once I could bring myself
to do it.

31:02.861 --> 31:04.361
I assume you're here
about condÃ©.

31:04.363 --> 31:06.263
In a way, yes.

31:06.265 --> 31:07.898
He is yours.

31:07.900 --> 31:10.033
You're free...

31:10.035 --> 31:12.069
To do as you please.

31:12.071 --> 31:14.605
I don't understand.

31:14.607 --> 31:16.874
What's changed?

31:18.610 --> 31:20.477
I cannot bear
to see you in pain.

31:20.479 --> 31:24.248
And I will not be the cause
of any more suffering.

31:24.250 --> 31:26.183
Even if your pain results
from being kept

31:26.185 --> 31:28.418
From another man
whom you desire.

31:28.420 --> 31:32.089
Francis...
It's best
that you don't interrupt.

31:32.091 --> 31:33.624
This is not easy or pleasant,

31:33.626 --> 31:35.559
And I'm not even sure
if it's wise.

31:35.561 --> 31:37.094
But if you sincerely believe

31:37.096 --> 31:39.329
That your best path
to healing is at his side,

31:39.331 --> 31:41.164
I will not stand in your way.

31:42.567 --> 31:46.570
You may remain at court
with condÃ© with my protection.

31:46.572 --> 31:49.139
Don't make me regret this, mary.

31:49.141 --> 31:51.308
For god's sake, be careful.

31:51.310 --> 31:53.043
Just don't be seen with him.

31:54.178 --> 31:56.480
I will protect you
as best I can,

31:56.482 --> 31:59.416
Silence any rumors I'm able to.

31:59.418 --> 32:01.485
But if there is ever proof...

32:01.487 --> 32:03.420
If we are caught
together, you mean.

32:03.422 --> 32:06.223
If there is a child.

32:10.295 --> 32:11.595
I'm sorry we've come to this.

32:11.597 --> 32:13.664
Mm.

32:13.666 --> 32:15.933
Well, it's as you
suggested months ago.

32:17.669 --> 32:19.303
Let us hope that this allows

32:19.305 --> 32:22.005
One of us to be happy at least.

32:40.191 --> 32:42.459
Ask for baron eduard at the
ball, and tell him you're

32:42.461 --> 32:44.962
Seeking his training in how to
become more skillful courtesans.

32:44.964 --> 32:47.030
That should flatter his ego.

32:47.032 --> 32:49.700
Teach us to be better whores?

32:49.702 --> 32:52.402
I like it.
Wish us luck.

32:58.343 --> 33:00.410
My, how the tables
have turned.

33:00.412 --> 33:03.146
Now it's you who fears
being seen with me.

33:03.148 --> 33:07.117
Greer, you all but announced
at that market that you are...

33:07.119 --> 33:09.353
A madam?

33:09.355 --> 33:11.488
I am, leith.
You must separate yourself

33:11.490 --> 33:12.756
From this trade,
from these women.

33:12.758 --> 33:14.358
I'm trapped

33:14.360 --> 33:16.994
In a marriage to a man
in prison for treason.

33:16.996 --> 33:18.295
I'm disgraced in the
eyes of the crown

33:18.297 --> 33:20.230
And most of this village.

33:20.232 --> 33:22.366
I have nothing
to offer any man.

33:22.368 --> 33:24.001
And little enough
to offer a friend.

33:24.003 --> 33:25.435
Except for the women
I'm helping.

33:25.437 --> 33:27.270
I can't give that up.

33:27.272 --> 33:29.172
Not even for your approval.

33:33.578 --> 33:36.513
It's a hard enough life without
seeing your disappointment.

33:36.515 --> 33:38.782
So I'll make it
easier on both of us

33:38.784 --> 33:41.318
And go elsewhere.

