â™ª let's be complete.

34:49.087 --> 34:50.821
I got word
that you were leaving.

34:50.823 --> 34:53.290
I'm finding this french
court extremely trying.

34:53.292 --> 34:56.226
I'd like to leave with at
least one prospect intact.

34:56.228 --> 34:57.694
Please tell me you've
ended things with mary,

34:57.696 --> 34:58.795
So I don't have to go back

34:58.797 --> 35:00.230
Inside and tell francis

35:00.232 --> 35:01.465
What you've been
doing with his wife.

35:01.467 --> 35:04.101
You told me
that blood, family...

35:04.103 --> 35:05.836
Is everything,
and I am your brother.

35:05.838 --> 35:08.738
I don't think
you'd risk my death.

35:08.740 --> 35:11.341
It is you who is taking
the risk, and for what?

35:11.343 --> 35:12.843
Love.

35:12.845 --> 35:15.212
Mary will never leave francis.

35:15.214 --> 35:18.115
She has a duty not only to
France, but to scotland.

35:18.117 --> 35:19.483
I don't need a lecture
on politics, antoine...

35:19.485 --> 35:20.650
Then on love.

35:20.652 --> 35:22.886
For theirs was
rumored to be great.

35:22.888 --> 35:25.355
If mary can turn away from
her husband after being married

35:25.357 --> 35:27.624
For less than a year,
then she is a fickle

35:27.626 --> 35:29.559
And foolish woman.

35:35.633 --> 35:39.302
That may have been your one
chance to harm a king and live.

35:42.240 --> 35:43.673
When this is over,

35:43.675 --> 35:45.909
You will be running
for your life.

35:45.911 --> 35:49.513
Having turned down the queen of
England, who will despise you,

35:49.515 --> 35:51.414
And been cast aside
by the queen of scots,

35:51.416 --> 35:53.550
Who will want you gone.

35:53.552 --> 35:56.219
Your parting will
happen slowly,

35:56.221 --> 35:59.656
By the way, as mary knows
you've risked your life.

35:59.658 --> 36:02.792
Oh, my guess is that she'll
inch back to her husband,

36:02.794 --> 36:05.529
Feeling guilty for
costing you your head.

36:05.531 --> 36:07.364
Because even mary knows

36:07.366 --> 36:09.799
That francis will find a
way to kill you for this.

36:09.801 --> 36:11.902
A knife in the back, perhaps.

36:11.904 --> 36:13.770
The valois way.

36:15.506 --> 36:18.875
Please... Be sensible, louis.

36:18.877 --> 36:20.744
Meet with elizabeth's envoy.

36:20.746 --> 36:23.547
Build a future
controlled by you,

36:23.549 --> 36:26.650
Not the changeable
heart of a woman.

36:27.919 --> 36:29.753
I have to go.

36:29.755 --> 36:31.421
I've left a parting gift

36:31.423 --> 36:33.790
For kenna and bash,
and soon I'll be

36:33.792 --> 36:35.892
Even less welcome
than I am now.

36:39.564 --> 36:40.830
Hyah!

36:47.838 --> 36:50.407
Bash, if you meant what you
said, and you'll take me

36:50.409 --> 36:51.841
To paris, then I would
like to go soon.

36:51.843 --> 36:52.976
Now, even.

36:52.978 --> 36:54.878
Someone left this letter
on my desk.

36:54.880 --> 36:57.581
It's addressed to the queen
of navarre, antoine's wife.

36:57.583 --> 36:59.916
It's an invitation
to the tasting.

36:59.918 --> 37:01.952
Written by you.

37:01.954 --> 37:05.655
Um... It must have been
dropped off here by a servant,

37:05.657 --> 37:07.324
After the queen presented it.

37:07.326 --> 37:09.659
Why did you invite her
in the first place?

37:09.661 --> 37:11.528
You write, "we do hope

37:11.530 --> 37:13.830
Your recent illness will not
prevent your attendance."

37:13.832 --> 37:15.599
What recent illness?

37:15.601 --> 37:17.867
Who told you the queen was sick?
Why was this left on my desk?

37:17.869 --> 37:19.869
Is it some kind
of coded message?

37:19.871 --> 37:21.671
Is this antoine's work?
Kenna, say something!

37:21.673 --> 37:24.341
Please stop!
Just stop!

37:25.610 --> 37:27.877
I'm so tired of all the lies.

37:27.879 --> 37:30.814
Of making you believe
I'm someone I'm not.

37:32.617 --> 37:34.751
He asked me to marry him, bash.

37:34.753 --> 37:36.686
He said he'd make me a queen.

37:36.688 --> 37:38.455
He was lying, of course.

37:38.457 --> 37:40.457
But I was ready to say yes.

37:40.459 --> 37:42.359
I wanted it.

37:42.361 --> 37:44.561
I wanted a different life.

37:44.563 --> 37:46.329
I wanted things you
could never give me.

37:46.331 --> 37:48.665
And never can.

37:52.036 --> 37:54.804
Then there is no reason
for me to be here.

38:07.685 --> 38:09.886
(door closes)

38:14.925 --> 38:17.494
(baby cooing)

38:26.937 --> 38:29.806
Look at that forehead.

38:29.808 --> 38:31.808
So smooth.

38:31.810 --> 38:33.677
Free of worry.

38:33.679 --> 38:35.545
Ah, I envy him of that.

38:35.547 --> 38:36.813
I do, too.

38:38.849 --> 38:41.318
I thought you'd
want to know that I...

38:41.320 --> 38:42.886
I took your advice.

38:44.088 --> 38:45.955
I let mary go.

38:45.957 --> 38:47.424
You did?

38:47.426 --> 38:48.758
I did.

38:48.760 --> 38:50.694
I hated it,
every moment of it.

38:50.696 --> 38:53.029
But now, somehow I...
I feel better.

38:53.031 --> 38:55.065
Awful, but better.

38:56.701 --> 38:58.101
You are a kind

38:58.103 --> 38:59.903
And selfless man.

39:01.572 --> 39:04.107
And you were right.

39:04.109 --> 39:05.909
As you so often are.

39:05.911 --> 39:09.879
Now that mary is free
to move on without me...

39:09.881 --> 39:13.383
I find that I'm free
to do the same.

39:13.385 --> 39:15.785
Lately I've found that...

39:15.787 --> 39:19.456
The only times that I feel truly
safe in this castle, untaxed,

39:19.458 --> 39:22.692
Unworried and... Peaceful

39:22.694 --> 39:23.960
As this lucky child here,

39:23.962 --> 39:26.563
Is when I'm with you.

39:28.065 --> 39:30.400
Francis, no.

39:32.670 --> 39:34.637
We both still love mary.

39:34.639 --> 39:35.739
(sighs)

39:35.741 --> 39:37.540
And who knows?

39:37.542 --> 39:40.510
When she finds the strength
to truly love again,

39:40.512 --> 39:43.613
You may find you're not as
free from her as you think.

39:51.055 --> 39:53.590
(knock at door)

39:53.592 --> 39:55.091
Louis, come in quickly.

39:55.093 --> 39:57.694
I got your summons.
I was worried.

39:57.696 --> 40:00.029
Francis has had
a change of heart.

40:00.031 --> 40:01.664
He's not going
to stand in our way.

40:01.666 --> 40:03.666
We have to be discreet,
of course, but...

40:03.668 --> 40:05.869
As soon as we go to scotland...
Well, there's no need to rush

40:05.871 --> 40:07.737
Our departure now.
We can be cautious.

40:07.739 --> 40:09.406
How cautious?

40:09.408 --> 40:10.707
Why?

40:10.709 --> 40:13.610
What if francis changes
his mind again?

40:13.612 --> 40:16.780
What if this promise
of safety here is fleeting?

40:16.782 --> 40:18.948
Francis has given this
much painful thought.

40:18.950 --> 40:20.784
He didn't make this
decision easily.

40:20.786 --> 40:22.185
Exactly!

40:22.187 --> 40:24.154
What man, what king, would
give another man his wife?

40:24.156 --> 40:25.688
Mary, we need
to get out of here.

40:25.690 --> 40:27.824
You do realize that
even in scotland,

40:27.826 --> 40:29.592
We would have to be discreet.

40:29.594 --> 40:30.860
Of course I understand that.

40:30.862 --> 40:32.796
But you would be queen
of your own nation.

40:32.798 --> 40:34.864
You would have some
additional freedom.

40:34.866 --> 40:37.100
Unless you're having second
thoughts of leaving at all.

40:37.102 --> 40:38.802
We are going to scotland.

40:38.804 --> 40:41.604
I am needed there, and
I want you at my side.

40:42.973 --> 40:44.774
I love you.

40:46.444 --> 40:48.445
How do you feel about francis?

40:48.447 --> 40:50.113
You don't think this

40:50.115 --> 40:52.215
Act of unprecedented
generosity

40:52.217 --> 40:54.751
Is a trick somehow?

40:54.753 --> 40:57.120
Francis has only ever
wanted to protect me.

40:57.122 --> 40:58.688
Because he loves you.

40:58.690 --> 40:59.889
Because he wants you back.

40:59.891 --> 41:01.991
He's doing this to win you back.

41:01.993 --> 41:03.460
I can hear you soften
toward him.

41:03.462 --> 41:07.230
You and I have
made plans together.

41:07.232 --> 41:09.566
And that hasn't changed.

41:09.568 --> 41:10.934
But we need to trust each other.

41:13.704 --> 41:16.239
Do we trust each other?

41:16.241 --> 41:18.107
All right.

41:18.109 --> 41:20.076
Of course, I trust you.

41:31.255 --> 41:33.690
She'll be pleased to hear
what you've told me today.

41:33.692 --> 41:35.725
A marriage alliance
like this would be

41:35.727 --> 41:37.093
A boon to her people...

41:37.095 --> 41:38.561
And yours.

41:38.563 --> 41:41.264
Please send her
my warmest personal regards.

41:41.266 --> 41:42.599
From what I've been told,

41:42.601 --> 41:44.133
There's no queen more beautiful,

41:44.135 --> 41:47.804
Gracious or wise than elizabeth.

